170
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:27,880
Und der Preis geht an Mare Pritti.

171
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,320
- Gott!
- Toledo Truth Teller.

172
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,480
Ja!

173
